name: AES.KeyWrap
desc: An implementation of AES Key Wrapping in accordance with the IETF RFC 3394 specification.

items.name: static func wrap(SymmetricKey, using: SymmetricKey) -> Data
items.desc: Wraps a key using the AES wrap algorithm.
